{"tid":1399119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】美國會人權委員會促請停售軍火及防暴裝備給香港警察","createTime":"2019-08-03T05:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:44:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e98612d63b042a5d35d4beaf53d776102f88a026","tid":1399119,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】美國會人權委員會促請停售軍火及防暴裝備給香港警察<br />\n<br />\n國會人權委員會主席眾議員史密斯(Christopher Smith)和麥高文(James McGovern)致函國務卿蓬佩奧(Mike Pompeo)及商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross），要求停止出售軍火及人群控制和防暴裝備給香港警方，並公開表明美國不會對香港內部鎮壓和平示威提供協助。香港警方被批評對反政府示威者使用過度武力。<br />\n<br />\n兩位議員又要求白宮對香港與中國政府把示威定性為「暴動」及指控美國幕後策劃作出反擊，指香港目前的政治動盪是自己一手造成。國務院與商務部未對委員會的要求作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n「香港眾志」秘書長黃之鋒本周曾在Twitter發帖文，上載香港警方向示威者發射的催淚彈和橡膠子彈照片。<br />\n路透社<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"c3ef4549c96209cd1e0834945443b0aaba3030ed","tid":1399119,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fffc02d52cb2de19ea0e671931776b48e0e8f97","tid":1399119,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293c1c7a04b0d4982c7e5e1f86ea1770e1b2aaf6","tid":1399119,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsSYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=e8ac1b31\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses</a><br />\n已達100,000